aboutme.title: About Me
aboutme.content: Hey im Dominik one of the first Platformengineer apprenticeships in Switzerland. I like to work on my homelab in my freetime. In summer 2021 I started my apprenticeship at UBS AG and gained some skills in our digital world
aboutme.content2: If you are interested in some things i do, just check my Repositories on my GitHub. If you dare to challenge yourself try to clone the Repository and rebuild my Project.
aboutme.content3: If you find undocumented errors feel free to open a Issue or contact me.
